<emphasis bold="true" box="[170,304,534,563]" pageId="150" pageNumber="752">Breeding.</emphasis>
No information.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[169,1217,569,603]" pageId="150" pageNumber="752" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="150.[168,1376,260,726]" box="[169,1217,569,603]" pageId="150" pageNumber="752">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[169,404,569,603]" pageId="150" pageNumber="752">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Yalden’s Rat is presumably nocturnal and partly arboreal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[170,1110,608,642]" pageId="150" pageNumber="752" type="biology_ecology">
